dependencies.name: xunit
dependencies.description:
xUnit.net is a developer testing framework, built to support Test Driven Development, with a design goal of extreme simplicity and alignment with framework features.

Installing this package installs xunit.core, xunit.assert, and xunit.analyzers.

dependencies.name: xunit.abstractions
dependencies.description: Common abstractions used to exchange information between xUnit.net and version-independent runners (xunit.abstractions.dll).

dependencies.name: xunit.analyzers
dependencies.description: Code Analyzers for projects using xUnit.net that help find and fix frequent issues when writing tests.

dependencies.name: xunit.assert
dependencies.description: Includes the assertion library from xUnit.net (xunit.assert.dll). Supports .NET Standard 1.1.

dependencies.name: xunit.core
dependencies.description: Includes the libraries for writing unit tests with xUnit.net.

dependencies.name: xunit.extensibility.core
dependencies.description: Includes xunit.core.dll for extensibility purposes. Supports .NET 4.5.2 or later, and .NET Standard 1.1.

dependencies.name: xunit.extensibility.execution
dependencies.description: Includes xunit.execution.*.dll for extensibility purposes. Supports .NET 4.5.2 or later, and .NET Standard 1.1.
